        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat: add Cloudflare Dynamic Workers provider",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nImplements Cloudflare Dynamic Workers as a new module-runtime provider distinct from the existing Cloudflare Containers provider.\n\n- adds `worker-runtime` provider target support and delegated module-run script validation\n- adds the `cloudflare-dynamic-workers` provider with aliases `cf-dynamic` and `cfdw`\n- adds a Dynamic Workers loader Worker with authenticated readiness/run/status/list/logs/delete endpoints\n- documents setup, config, CLI usage, lifecycle behavior, and opt-in live smoke proof\n- adds an opt-in live smoke harness that is non-mutating unless explicit live gates are set\n\nCloses #283.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `go test ./internal/providers/cloudflaredynamicworkers ./internal/providers/all ./internal/cli`\n- `go test -race ./internal/providers/cloudflaredynamicworkers ./internal/providers/all ./internal/cli`\n- `go test ./internal/providers/cloudflare ./internal/providers/azuredynamicsessions`\n- `npm run format:check --prefix worker`\n- `npm run lint --prefix worker`\n- `npm run check --prefix worker`\n- `npm test --prefix worker -- cloudflare-dynamic-worker-runner`\n- `npm test --prefix worker -- cloudflare-container-runner`\n- `npm run build:cloudflare-dynamic-workers --prefix worker`\n- `npm run build --prefix worker`\n- `node --test scripts/deploy-cloudflare-dynamic-workers-smoke.test.js`\n- `scripts/deploy-cloudflare-dynamic-workers-smoke.sh` -> `environment_blocked provider=cloudflare-dynamic-workers mutation=false reason=live_gate_missing`\n- `node scripts/check-docs-links.mjs`\n- `node scripts/check-command-docs.mjs`\n- `go vet ./...`\n- `~/.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode branch --base origin/main` -> clean, no accepted/actionable findings\n",
